# Monorepo environment glossary (copy per-app; do not commit real secrets)
#
# apps/mobile       — EXPO_PUBLIC_GOOGLE_MAPS_API_KEY, EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, EXPO_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# apps/admin        — NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_URL, NEXT_PUBLIC_SUPABASE_ANON_KEY
# apps/backend      — DATABASE_URL, DIRECT_URL, SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_JWT_SECRET, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY, PORT, CORS_ORIGINS
